<section class="timeline-sec">
  <div class="wrap-wide">
    <div class="timeline-head">
      <span class="eyebrow">From kiln to kitchen</span>
      <h2>How <em>IONIQ</em> got here.</h2>
      <p>Two years from the first founding memo to the first box shipped.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="timeline">
      <div class="timeline-item is-key"><span class="dot"></span><div><div class="yr">Jan 2024</div><h4>The founding memo</h4><p>The original observation: people are buying four supplements to chase symptoms that aren't getting better. Most aren't aging — they're depleting.</p></div></div>
      <div class="timeline-item"><span class="dot"></span><div><div class="yr">Apr 2024</div><h4>The first salt trial</h4><p>We tested 23 commercial salts — sea, Himalayan, Celtic, lake — looking for one with a mineral profile that could anchor a real formula.</p></div></div>
      <div class="timeline-item is-key"><span class="dot"></span><div><div class="yr">Aug 2024</div><h4>First trip to Korea</h4><p>Spent six weeks visiting traditional bamboo-salt kilns. Came back convinced 9× was the only product that could carry the formula.</p></div></div>
      <div class="timeline-item"><span class="dot"></span><div><div class="yr">Dec 2024</div><h4>Formulation locked</h4><p>14+ ingredients across four supplement categories. Every dose clinical. Every milligram on the label.</p></div></div>
      <div class="timeline-item"><span class="dot"></span><div><div class="yr">Mar 2025</div><h4>Clinical pilot — n=24</h4><p>Independent lab measured plasma volume, RPE and recovery markers in 24 athletes. 64% improvement in hydration vs water.</p></div></div>
      <div class="timeline-item is-key"><span class="dot"></span><div><div class="yr">Sep 2025</div><h4>First box ships</h4><p>IONIQ Bamboo Salt Elixir — Lemon — ships from our Brooklyn warehouse. Launch month sells out in three weeks.</p></div></div>
      <div class="timeline-item"><span class="dot"></span><div><div class="yr">Q3 2026</div><h4>New flavours</h4><p>Watermelon and Blueberry launch. Sour Mango drops in Q4.</p></div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
